                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/af0f65f4-f94d-11e4-b150-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/af0f65f4-f94d-11e4-b150-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_54 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;request on 0x400000401:0x1bd:0x0 is not FAILED on mds1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: shadow-21vm8 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdt.lustre-MDT0000.hsm.actions | awk &apos;/&apos;0x400000401:0x1bd:0x0&apos;.*action=&apos;ARCHIVE&apos;/ {print \$13}&apos; | cut -f2 -d=
Update not seen after 200s: wanted &apos;FAILED&apos; got &apos;&apos;
 sanity-hsm test_54: @@@@@@ FAIL: request on 0x400000401:0x1bd:0x0 is not FAILED on mds1 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
